  "text": "\"This is the nature of a true companion device. Unlike a laptop, the added advantages of pocket size, minimal weight, and an instant-on, instant-off capability allow Handhelds to fit seamlessly into student lifestyles characterized by dynamic and intermittent study opportunities\". [CITATION_1] We build upon the prior studies in three ways.",
